{
  "stem": "15991.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it's barely, it's a little bit over a month.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That she prepared us for this move.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was organized by a Jewish organization who organized the Kindertransport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't ask me for the name, I'm not quite sure of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you had to apply for this, and, I imagine, pay quite a bit of money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I not-- wasn't sure of the details.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I Was 14, you really are still very immature and--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, to say that we would live with my aunt, that life would be a lot different, and to try and make life as easy as possible for her and be good children, in other words.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that they would try and return as soon as possible and come that way too as soon as possible, as soon as my father would be released.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, nobody knew when that would be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or if that would be.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or if that would be.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a lot of children did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The evening before we left, of course, a lot of relatives and friends came to say goodbye and brought lovely presents, which then we couldn't take along because we were only allowed to a little suitcase to take with us.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as far as I know, it was only one-- one mark or 10 marks, probably 10 marks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember one mark, but I think that would be too little.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It could have been.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the morning of the transport when we were supposed to go to the station, my brother had a terrible stomachache.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so wife my mother called a doctor, because our doctor no longer was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she called a Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Stone, who later became my stepfather-in-law.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
